item.title: Project II: SQL Data exploration
item.description: In this I have explored the dataset which contains the information of covid deaths and covid vaccinations. Data exploration and data cleaning was done in SQL server.The dataset has been taken from “Our world in data” The data gives brief explanation about the covid deaths and covid vaccinations which is presented as dashboard and compared across various data attributes. Link to Github repository

item.title: Project I: CovidDashboard
item.description: In this I have created a dashboard which contains the information of covid deaths and covid vaccinations. The dashboard is created in Tableau.The dataset has been taken from “Our world in data” The data gives brief explanation about the covid deaths and covid vaccinations which is presented as dashboard and compared across various data attributes. [Link to the project] (https://public.tableau.com/app/profile/tejasswini4008/viz/CovidDashboard_16613261223790/Dashboard1)
